  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Techniques: Black, Blue, Green, Red </p><p></p><p>You install a mechanism to restrain its targets.</p><p> When your puppet attempts to grapple a creature, it applies your Proficiency Bonus to the roll (or twice your Proficiency Bonus if the Puppet Tool already has this ability).</p><p> When you successfully grapple a creature with this upgrade, the target creature is restrained, and your puppet still has the rest of its appendages for other uses.</p><p> Additionally, it can move its restrained target without any reduction of its movement speed.</p><p></p>",
